                {
                    "subtitle": "What we have reviewed",
                    "components": [
                        {
                            "type": "text-paragraph",
                            "text": "Learning in practice is structural different to learning in the classroom. Students are entitled to support from their educators and could have reasonable adjustments provided they can meet the competencies set out in the standards of proficiency."
                        }
